snippet.title: The Rise of the Dough - Pirate Software's 14th Game Jam Entry - Full playthrough
snippet.description:
A little game we made as an entry for the 14th Pirate Software Game Jam. Pretty happy how it turned out. You can try it out at ratsanddogs.itch.io/the-rise-of-the-doughIf you end up trying it feedback would be appreciated :D

Song playing during gameplay:
Happy Arcade Tune by rezoner
